snippet.title: Persona Q: Shadow of the Labyrinth: Opening Movie
snippet.description:
The Persona-users cross time and space to assemble as a new tale unfolds...

Coming 11/25/2014 for Nintendo 3DS.

For more information: http://www.atlus.com/personaq/
